property.name: Text
property.value: Hail and well met, brave traveler! The door in front of you will bring you closer to your goal. The door behind it will too, but behind that door is Martin. Martin's a... bit of a talker. But he means well, and he will undoubtedly help you in your quest. J.M.

property.name: Text
property.value: Use the arrow buttons or WASD to move, and Space to jump. Press Enter (or Up/Down) to interact.
